0buying%20home%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20pretty%20much%20bought%20everything%20at%20Lowe's%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20bulk%20buying%2C%20so%20we%20got%20really%20good%20discounts%2C%20and%20they%20had%20some%20good%20sales%20on%20appliances.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeidecker%20added%20that%20it%20felt%20like%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20they%20went%20to%20Lowe's%20daily%20to%20ensure%20they%20were%20taking%20advantage%20of%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20bought%20a%20few%20things%20that%20were%20on%20sale%20for%20Black%20Friday%20and%20on%20Amazon%2C%20so%20we%20got%20good%20deals%20on%20that%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20small%20things%20Heidecker%20would%20change%20about%20the%20space%20if%20she%20could.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20stands%20on%20a%20couch%20to%20hang%20a%20painting%20above%20a%20couch.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6957dc68832e0ef1ead712ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221332%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EYeli%20Heidecker%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20probably%20could%20have%20made%20it%20slightly%20bigger%20but%20kept%20it%20within%20the%20same%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20Heidecker%20said%2C%20particularly%20because%20she%20plans%20for%20her%20mom%20to%20age%20in%20the%20space%20and%20would%20want%20it%20to%20be%20easily%20suited%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcant-retire-social-security-working-at-84-financial-struggle-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewheelchair%20use%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20needed%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20plan%20on%20her%20being%20with%20us%20forever%2C%20as%20far%20as%20I%20know%2C%20and%20we%20just%20never%20know%20where%20her%20health%20could%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Heidecker%20added.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20just%20a%2