C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20year%20of%20his%20second%20term%20has%20shown%20mixed%20results%20for%20the%20business%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI%20industry%20surged%2C%20while%20the%20retail%20sector%20struggled%20under%20tariffs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20industries%2C%20like%20manufacturing%2C%20have%20fallen%20short%20of%20expectations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20year%20in%20office%20was%20a%20mixed%20bag%20of%20blessings%20and%20woes%20for%20the%20business%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20began%20with%20a%20lineup%20of%20billionaires%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-inauguration-ceo-guests-bezos-zuckerberg-musk-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump's%20inauguration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20soon%20saw%20their%20net%20worth%20diminish%20after%20Trump%20enacted%20sweeping%20tariffs%20aimed%20at%20reshoring%20manufacturing%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20fortunes%20soon%20rebounded%2C%20and%20Trump%C2%A0has%20been%20a%20booster%20of%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20which%20continued%20to%20grow%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusinesses%20were%20also%20often%20caught%20in%20Trump's%20crosshairs%2C%20including%20Intel%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Walmart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20retail%20sector%20to%20the%20AI%20industry%2C%20here's%20how%20different%20industries%20fared%20in%20Trump's%20first%20year%20of%20his%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a14b893e-1e71-46f9-9e84-b9a3c42f34eb%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20industry%20continued%20to%20soar%20during%20the%20first%20year%20of%20Trump's%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Morningstar%2C%20the%20company's%20AI%20basket%20of%2034%20stocks%2C%20which%20includes%20Amazon%2C%20Cisco%2C%20and%20Apple%2C%20saw%20a%2050.8%25%20in%20share%20value%20in%202025%2C%20while%20the%20overall%20stock%20market%20gained%2017.3%25%20and%20the%20broader%20tech%20sector%20rose%2021.4%25%2C%20based%20on%20the%20Morningstar%20US%20Market%20Index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20first%20month%20of%20his%20presidency%2C%20Trump%20announced%20a%20%24500%20billion%20AI%20infrastructure%20project%20called%20Stargate%2C%20to%20be%20led%20by%20OpenAI%2C%20Oracle%2C%20and%20SoftBank%2C%20which%20he%20said%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20largest%20AI%20infrastructure%20project%20in%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20also%20been%20a%20booster%20of%20the%20tech%20industry%20at%20large%20%E2%80%94%20while%20receiving%20donations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-cook-donald-trump-gift-apple-tariffs-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egifts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pledges%20for%20more%20American%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhos-who-tech-leaders-attended-dinner-white-house-altman-pichai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epraise%20from%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20had%20notable%20visits%20with%20CEOs%2C%20including%20Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang.%20The%20US%20eventually%20allowed%20Nvidia%20to%20sell%20H200%20chips%20to%20China%2C%20under%20the%20condition%20that%20the%20government%20gets%20a%20cut%20of%20the%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20rescinded%20an%20executive%20order%20issued%20by%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20that%C2%A0established%20a%20federal%20framework%20for%20AI%20safety%20and%20risk%20mitigation%2C%C2%A0and%20he%20signed%20a%20new%20order%20intended%20to%20override%20state-level%20AI%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20after%20publicly%20calling%20for%20the%20resignation%20of%20Intel's%20CEO%2C%20Trump%20made%20a%20deal%20for%20the%20US%20to%20take%20a%20nearly%2010%25%20equity%20in%20the%20company%2C%20which%20has%20since%20seen%20its%20stock%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20what%20Trump's%20second%20year%20in%20office%20in%20his%20second%20term%20will%20