E%3Cli%3EThe%20auction%20was%20entirely%20online%2C%20and%20people%20placed%20115%20bids%20without%20kicking%20the%20tires%20in%20person.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20what%20happened%20in%20real%20life%20%E2%80%94%20a%20four-year%20process%20ending%20when%20the%20%26quot%3Bgavel%26quot%3B%20fell%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20auction%20off%20a%20former%20billionaire's%20armor-plated%20Mercedes%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20virtually%20every%20bankruptcy%20auction%20these%20days%2C%20there's%20a%20one-word%20answer%20to%20that%20question%20%E2%80%94%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20followed%20the%20auction%20of%20a%20Mercedes-Benz%20Maybach%20S650%2C%20kicking%20the%20tires%20in%20person%20and%20watching%20the%20virtual%20action%20as%20it%20sold%20online%20to%20its%20115th%20bidder%2C%20for%20%2463%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20shows%20just%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20for%20buyers%20to%20purchase%20%E2%80%94%20sight%20unseen%20%E2%80%94%20the%20cars%2C%20motorcycles%2C%20even%20the%20cast-off%20wall%20sconces%20and%20used%20vacuum%20cleaners%20of%20the%20nouveau%20poor.%20All%20that's%20needed%20is%20an%20internet%20connection%20and%20the%20winning%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20a%20small%20army%20of%20lawyers%2C%20bankruptcy%20judges%2C%20appraisers%2C%20and%20auctioneers%20labor%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%20It%20took%20four%20years%20of%20real-life%20effort%20before%20the%20virtual%20gavel%20fell%20on%20Thursday%2C%20and%20the%20Mercedes%20found%20its%20new%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20the%20journey%20of%20a%20billionaire's%20luxury%20sedan%20%E2%80%94%20from%20a%20showroom%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20to%20a%20tow%20lot%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20finally%20to%20the%20yard%20of%20a%20Connecticut%20auction%20house%2C%20where%20almost%20no%20one%20bothered%20to%20see%20the%20car%20in%20person%20before%20bidding%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20to%20own%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228257%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Knudson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696a4ca4764ca5f34d2a90e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225505%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAuctioneer%20Mike%20Knudson%20shows%20off%20the%20amenities%20of%20a%202018%20Mercedes-Benz%20Maybach%20S650.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Buglewicz%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20some%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mercedes-Benz%20was%20once%20the%20shiny%20new%20chauffeured%20conveyance%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-bankruptcy-miles-guo-wengui-yacht-mansions-auction-block-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMiles%20Guo%2C%20who%20declared%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy%20in%20early%202022%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguo-wengui-steve-bannon-ally-arrested-charged-fraud-scheme-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGuo%20was%20arrested%20a%20year%20later%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20remains%20in%20jail%20pending%20his%20Manhattan%20sentencing%20for%20a%20%241.3%20billion%20fraud%20and%20racketeering-conspiracy%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECourt%20records%20show%20that%20Guo%20bought%20the%20car%20new%20in%202018%2C%20for%20%24192%2C000%2C%20at%20a%20Mercedes-Benz%20showroom%20just%20south%20of%20Lincoln%20Center%20in%20Manhattan.%20It%20was%2C%20relatively%20speaking%2C%20one%20of%20his%20economy%20cars.%20Federal%20prosecutors%20said%20Guo's%20custom%20Bugatti%20Chiron%2C%20his%20costliest%20ride%2C%20was%20purchased%20for%20%244.4%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miles%20Guo%20in%20his%20NYC%20apartment%20in%202017%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6960fd6c04eda4732f2ec423%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223604%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMiles%20Guo%20in%20his%20NYC%20apartment%20in%202017%3Cp%3ETIMOTHY%20A.%20CLARY%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four-door%20Benz%20was%20built%20for%20luxury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20mini-bar%20back%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20auctioneer%20Mike%20Knudson%20said%2C%20giving%20Business%20Insider%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20car%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20car%20was%20parked%20outside%20The%20Hamilton%20Group%2C%20the%20Connecticut%20auction%20and%20appraisal%20company%20he%20runs%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Amy%20Maklari.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnudson%20leaned%20into%20the%20back%20seat%20and%20popped%20the%20door%20on%20the%20empty%20fridge%20between%20the%20rear%20seats.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20small%20bottles%2C%26quot%3B%20Knudson%20said%2C%20estimating%20its%20capacity.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20a%20Coke%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mercedes'%20amenities%20also%20include%20a%20small%20jar%20that%20Knudson%20discovered%20only%20Wednesday%2C%20in%20the%20glove%20compartment%2C%20set%20inside%20a%20recessed%20holder%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bflacon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%2C%20pulling%20the%20jar%20out.%20The%20smear%20of%20amber-colored%20gum%20inside%20was%20scent%20for%20the%20Mercedes'%20diffuser%20system%2C%20controllable%20through%20high%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20low%20settings%20on%20the%20dashboard%20computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20car%20dashboard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696a4c3e764ca5f34d2a90de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224965%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInside%20the%20Mercedes-Benz%2C%20one%20day%20before%20it%20was%20auctioned%20off%20to%20pay%20the%20bankruptcy%20debts%20of%20former%20billionaire%20Miles%20Guo.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Buglewicz%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAroma%20therapy%2C%26quot%3B%20Knudson%20joked%2C%20returning%20the%20jar%2C%20labeled%20%26quot%3BAgarwood%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20its%20holder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car%20was%20built%20for%20safety%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuo%20paid%20extra%20to%20have%20a%20German%20company%20install%20armor%20plating%20and%20bulletproof%20glass%20throughout.%20%26quot%3BSee%20how%20thick%20this%20glass%20is%3F%26quot%3B%20Knudson%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20lowering%20one%20of%20the%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuo's%20bankruptcy%20trustee%20has%20spent%20years%20demonstrating%20the%20true%20ownership%20of%20Guo's%20cars%2C%20planes%2C%20and%20mansions%2C%20and%20linking%20these%20assets%20back%20to%20Guo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mercedes%2C%20just%20one%20small%20piece%20of%20the%20bankruptcy%20puzzle%2C%20had%20been%20listed%20as%20an%20asset%20held%20by%20a%20Hong%20Kong-based%20shell%20company%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Guo's%20son%20and%2C%20briefly%2C%20his%20chauffeur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227996%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mercedes%20Benz%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696a4cf604eda4732f2f319c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mercedes%20on%20display%20for%20public%20inspection%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20at%20the%20Hamilton%20Group%2C%20LLC%20auction%20house%20in%20Clinton%2C%20Connecticut.%20%3Cp%3EJoe%20Buglewicz%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Guo's%20arrest%2C%20the%20car%20wound%20up%20abandoned%20in%20a%20New%20Jersey%20tow%20lot.%20It%20had%20to%20be%20moved%20via%20flatbed%20to%20the%20Hamilton%20Group's%20yard%20in%20Clinton%2C%20Connecticut%2C%20a%20half-hour%20east%20of%20New%20Haven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Knudson%20another%20month%20or%20so%20to%20ready%20the%20car%20for%20auction.%20He%20needed%20to%20obtain%20a%20bond%2C%20replace%20the%20battery%2C%20and%20get%20an%20electronic%20key%20fob%20made%20by%20Mercedes-Benz%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20when%20I%20learned%20it's%20pronounced%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EMy%3C%2Fem%3E-bach%2C%26quot%3B%20not%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EMay%3C%2Fem%3E-bach%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Knudson%2C%20who%20has%20also%20auctioned%20furnishings%20and%20knick-knacks%20from%20Guo's%20Manhattan%20penthouse%20and%20his%20fleet%20of%20high-end%20motorcycles%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bone%20Ducati%2C%20two%20BMWs%2C%20and%20three%20Harleys%2C%26quot%3B%20Maklari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d0717ea-b84a-4d66-a6e7-3adf3bc475d3%5C%22%3EThe%20bidding%20war%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWednesday%20was%20the%20only%20day%20during%20the%20ten-day%20auction%20that%20the%20public%20could%20drop%20by%20without%20an%20appointment%20and%20personally%20examine%20the%20Mercedes.%20Not%20a%20single%20person%20showed%20up%2C%20besides%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnline%20the%20next%20day%2C%20though%2C%20the%20bidding%20for%20the%20car%2C%20which%20had%20just%2021%2C000%20miles%20on%20the%20odometer%2C%20was%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BidSpotter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696a4a8c64858d02d2187849%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225392%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBidSpotter's%20listing%20for%20the%20Mercedes%20lets%20potential%20bidders%20inspect%20the%20car%20%E2%80%94%20down%20to%20the%20roar%20of%20its%20engine%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20comfort%20of%20their%20computers.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Buglewicz%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty-four%20hours%20before%20the%20auction%20was%20to%20close%2C%20more%20than%2080%20bidders%20on%20BidSpotter.com%20had%20pushed%20the%20price%20up%20to%20%2438%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20hour%20of%20bidding%2C%20interest%20accelerated.%20In%20the%20last%20five%20minutes%2C%20bidding%20climbed%20suddenly%20in%20%241%2C000%20increments%20until%20it%20reached%20the%20winning%20bid%20of%20%2463%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20price%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Kelley%20Blue%20Book%20value%2C%20which%20sets%20the%20current%20resale%20value%20for%20a%202018%20Mercedes-Benz%20Maybach%20S650%20at%20%2462%2C400%20%E2%80%94%20not%20counting%20the%20custom%20armor%20plating%20and%20bullet-proof%20glass%20Guo%20had%20installed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20feel%20safe%20bidding%20on%20something%20so%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20without%20actually%20seeing%20it%20in%20person%20%E2%80%94%20because%20of%20the%20clarity%20of%20auction%20listings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mercedes'%20listing%20on%20BidSpotter%20included%2049%20photographs%20and%20a%20two-minute%20video.%20The%20clip%20shows%20Knudson%20popping%20the%20hood%20and%20trunk%2C%20and%20driving%20it%20around%20Hamilton%20Auction's%20front%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F-79hzknGo8I%3Fstart%3D2%26feature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22IMG%208998%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EPotential%20bidders%20could%20hear%20Knudson%20start%20and%20rev%20the%20car's%20engine%2C%20and%20watch%20as%20his%20camera%20lingered%20on%20a%20small%20ding%20in%20the%20rear%20right%20bumper%20and%20a%20hair-thin%2C%20vertical%20crack%20in%20the%20windshield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20dozens%20of%20online%20auction%20platforms%20catering%20to%20bankruptcies%2C%20estate%20sales%2C%20and%20companies%20and%20individuals%20with%20something%20to%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaklari%20ticked%20off%20a%20few%20names%20on%20Wednesday.%20AuctionNinja%20specializes%20in%20estates%20and%20furnishings.%20ProxiBid%20and%20BidSpotter%20deals%20in%20vehicles%20and%20heavy%20machinery.%20LiveAuctioneers%20handles%20collectibles%20and%20antiques.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20auctioneers%2C%20listing%20on%20these%20sites%20is%20an%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227853%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Knudson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696a4be2764ca5f34d2a90da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225235%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAuctioneer%20Mike%20Knudson%20set%20the%20opening%20bid%20on%20a%20bankrupt%20billionaire's%20Mercedes%20at%20a%20low-balled%20%2420%2C000%2C%20confident%20that%20bidding%20would%20rise%20to%20fair-market%20value%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20did.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Buglewicz%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKnudson%20said%20he%20had%20appraised%20the%20Mercedes%20very%20conservatively%2C%20at%20around%20%2435%2C000%2C%20for%20the%20bankruptcy%20trustee.%20But%20for%20the%20ten-day%20auction's%20launch%2C%20he%20had%20set%20the%20minimum%20bid%20at%20a%20strategically%20low-balled%20%2420%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20gets%20people%20engaged%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20risk%20to%20such%20lowballing%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMost%20assets%20will%20find%20their%20fair-market%20value%20these%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%20with%20the%20internet%2C%20to%20do%20their%20research.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car's%20new%20owner%20wished%20to%20remain%20anonymous.%20Whoever%20they%20are%2C%20they'll%20need%20to%20pay%20a%2015%25%20fee%20to%20the%20auction%20company%2C%20and%20are%20responsible%20for%20their%20own%20transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20proceeds%20will%20now%20go%20into%20the%20bankruptcy%20estate%2C%20where%20it%20will%20help%20pay%20off%20Guo's%20many%20creditors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20drop%20in%20the%20bucket%2C%20given%20that%20Guo's%20bankruptcy%20debts%20hover%20around%20half%20a%20billion%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20Mercedes-Benz%20won't%20help%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kevin%20Tung%2C%20the%20Queens%2C%20New%20York%2C%20lawyer%20for%20nine%20China-based%20contrac