shopping%20carts%20filled%20exclusively%20with%20Kirkland%20products%20against%20national%20brands%20to%20find%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20cutting%20costs%20on%20everyday%20items%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffounding-history-of-costco%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuying%20in%20bulk%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20buying%20store%20brands%20are%20both%20big%20ways%20to%20save.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20store%20brands%20in%20bulk%3F%20That's%20like%20a%20cheat%20code%20to%20maximizing%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20found%20in%20a%20price%20analysis%20that%20shopping%20at%20Costco%20was%20generally%20cheaper%20on%20a%20unit-cost%20basis%20than%20buying%20the%20same%20products%20from%20a%20traditional%20retailer.%20Depending%20on%20the%20item%20and%20how%20often%20it's%20purchased%2C%20the%20savings%20could%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-items-shoppers-say-pay-for-a-membership-fee-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffset%20the%20%2465%20annual%20membership%3C%2Fa%3E%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Costco%20members%20find%20the%20chain's%20own%20Kirkland%20Signature%20brand%20is%20the%20real%20ticket%20to%20getting%20the%20most%20bang%20for%20their%20buck%2C%20though.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20look%20at%20how%20cost-effective%20it%20is%20to%20buy%20Kirkland%20compared%20to%20the%20comparable%20name-brand%20products%20Costco%20carries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-end-costco-things-to-get-from-employee-kirkland-signature-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKirkland%20Signature%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20big%20business%20for%20Costco.%20The%20banner%20%E2%80%94%20which%20includes%20gasoline%2C%20meat%2C%20some%20liquor%20products%2C%20and%20a%20range%20of%20other%20categories%20%E2%80%94%20accounted%20for%20roughly%20a%20third%20of%20Costco's%20%24267%20billion%20in%20worldwide%20sales%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20out%20how%20much%20of%20a%20difference%20the%20choice%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-kirkland-name-brand-products-compared-pop-secret-nature-valley-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebetween%20national%20brands%20and%20Kirkland%3C%2Fa%3E%20Signature%20can%20make%2C%20I%20visited%20a%20local%20warehouse%20and%20compared%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20focused%20on%20in-store%20products%20that%20were%20near%20matches%20between%20Kirkland%20Signature%20and%20a%20national%20brand%20in%20terms%20of%20functionality%2C%20key%20ingredients%2C%20and%20other%20relevant%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Kirkland%20Signature%20brand%20offers%20dozens%20of%20products%2C%20not%20every%20product%20has%20a%20like-for-like%20alternative.%20Sometimes%20it's%20because%20Costco%20only%20carries%20a%20Kirkland%20Signature%20offering%20(like%20milk)%2C%20and%20sometimes%20the%20national%20brand%20is%20the%20only%20choice%20(like%20Cheerios).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20narrowed%20my%20list%20to%2017%20representative%20items%20and%20calculated%20the%20cost%20of%20an%20exclusively%20Kirkland%20Signature%20shopping%20cart%20compared%20with%20an%20exclusively%20national-brand%20cart.%20I%20also%20did%20the%20math%20to%20determine%20the%20price%20difference%20if%20the%20Kirkland%20Signature%20items%20were%20sold%20in%20matching%20pack%20sizes%20to%20the%20national%20brand%20versions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20cases%2C%20the%20shelf%20price%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-kirkland-signature-brand-drives-success-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKirkland%20Signature%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20lower%20than%20the%20branded%20option%2C%20but%20the%20real%20difference%20emerged%20when%20adjusting%20for%20the%20actual%20number%20of%20units%20per%20pack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20branded%20shopping%20cart%20clocked%20in%20at%20%24297%2C%20while%20the%20Kirkland%20cart%20was%20%2472%20less%20at%20%24215%20before%20discounts%20or%20taxes.%20(Many%20shelf%20labels%20at%20Costco%20have%20discounts%20baked%20in.)%20After%20adjusting%20for%20pack%20sizes%2C%20the%20Kirkland%20cart%20would%20come%20in%20around%20%24186%2C%20for%20an%20effective%20savings%20of%20%24111%20or%20about%2037%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-pharmacies-serve-everyone-even-pets-deep-discounts-members-only-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epharmacy%20section%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20acetaminophen%2C%20allergy%20pills%2C%20cold%20medicine%2C%20and%20fiber%20supplement%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20accounted%20for%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20dollar%20savings%20in%20my%20cart%20comparisons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20unit-price%20basis%2C%20the%20savings%20ranged%20from%200%25%20(apple%20sauce%20pouches)%20to%2089%25%20(allergy%20medication).%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20the%20unit%20prices%20for%20Kirkland%20Signature%20products%20were%2010%25%20to%2050%25%20lower%20than%20those%20of%20their%20national-brand%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20covering%20retail%20for%20years%20now.%20I've%20always%20been%20watchful%20about%20prices%2C%20and%20I'm%20mildly%20obsessed%20with%20store%20brands%2C%20but%20these%20numbers%20surprised%20me.%20This%20analysis%20shows%20how%20big%20a%20wallet%20impact%20can%20come%20from%20a%20few%20very%20simple%20choices%20in%20the%20shopping%20aisles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20on%20to%20see%20the%20breakdown%20of%20the%2017%20items%20I%20compared%20prices%20for%2C%20in%20order%20of%20savings%20per%20unit%20before%20discounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAllergy%20medication%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Allergy%20medication%20at%20Costco%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696a8858e1ba468a96aa3b6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2