ht%3D%5C%222807%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Selkirk%20co-founders%2C%20brothers%20Rob%20and%20Mike%20Barnes.%3Cp%3ESelkirk%20Sport%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESelkirk%20is%20a%20leading%20pickleball%20equipment%20brand.%20If%20you%20play%20the%20sport%2C%20chances%20are%20you%20or%20your%20opponent%20is%20wielding%20one%20of%20their%20sticks.%20The%20shipping%20department%20manager%2C%20who%20works%20out%20of%20the%20company's%2087%2C000-square-foot%20warehouse%2C%20told%20me%20they%20fulfill%20roughly%201%2C000%20orders%20a%20day%20and%20up%20to%202%2C500%20during%20the%20holiday%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20was%20founded%20in%202014%20by%20two%20brothers%2C%20Rob%20and%20Mike%20Barnes%2C%20and%20their%20father%2C%20Jim%2C%20well%20before%20pickleball%20became%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPickleball%20had%20a%20connotation%20of%20being%20a%20senior%20sport%20for%20a%20while%2C%26quot%3B%20Rob%20told%20me%20at%20the%20Selkirk%20headquarters%20in%20Coeur%20d'Alene%2C%20Idaho%2C%20where%20the%20brothers%20grew%20up%20and%20started%20their%20first%20business%20as%20teens%20selling%20airsoft%20guns%20out%20of%20their%20dad's%20basement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20sold%20the%20airsoft%20business%20to%20pivot%20to%20pickleball%2C%20a%20game%20they%20discovered%20in%202009%20and%20couldn't%20get%20enough%20of.%20It%20seemed%20impossible%20that%20it%20wouldn't%20take%20off.%20They%20were%20right%20about%20that%2C%20but%20it%20took%20years%2C%20and%20a%20global%20pandemic%20that%20encouraged%20socially%20distant%20activities%2C%20before%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20would%20catch%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpickleball-average-age-popular-millenial-need-courts-fill-demand-report-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20sport%20has%20exploded%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20has%20the%20competition.%20The%20Barnes%20brothers%20believe%20in%20staying%20ahead%20by%20continuing%20to%20invest%20in%20R%26amp%3BD%20and%20deliver%20premium%20products.%20They%20have%20the%20only%20private%20sports%20science%20lab%20in%20pickleball%2C%20which%20they've%20invested%20roughly%20%241%20million%20into%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20few%20private%20sports%20labs%20in%20racket%20sports%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20youngest%20Barnes%20brother%2C%20Tom%2C%20joined%20the%20family%20business%20after%20a%20career%20in%20the%20Marines.%20He's%20the%20director%20of%20R%26amp%3BD%20and%20spent%20nearly%20three%20hours%20walking%20me%20through%20the%20lab%2C%20explaining%20in%20detail%20how%20each%20machine%20works%20and%20why%20it's%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224643%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22selkirk%20sport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696abe76a645d11881878d84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223482%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETom%20Barnes%20is%20a%20co-owner%20of%20Selkrik%20and%20the%20director%20of%20R%26amp%3BD.%3Cp%3ESelkirk%20Sport%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20paddle%20is%20their%20hero%20product%2C%20Selkirk%20also%20makes%20shoes%2C%20apparel%2C%20balls%2C%20and%20nets%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Beverything%20except%20the%20court%20surface%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tom%2C%20as%20long%20as%20it's%20in%20the%20pickleball%20realm.%20He%20and%20his%20brothers%20don't%20have%20any%20interest%20in%20expanding%20into%20the%20myriad%20of%20racket%20sports%3A%20tennis%2C%20padel%2C%20squash%2C%20etc.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20only%20ever%20do%20pickleball.%20This%20was%20intentional%20from%20day%20one.%20It's%20called%20Selkirk%20Sport%3B%20it's%20not%20called%20Selkirk%20Sports.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETom%20greeted%20me%20at%20the%20unassuming%20entrance%20of%20the%20facility%2C%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3BAqua.%26quot%3B%20It%20makes%20up%20about%2022%2C000%20square%20feet%20of%20Selkirk's%20160%2C000-square-foot%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22selkirk%20sport%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696aa192c58df2ecd5ccb610%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lab%20portion%20of%20the%20building%2C%20which%20has%20been%20up%20and%20running%20for%20about%20a%20year%2C%20is%20split%20into%20two%20rooms.%20We%20started%20in%20the%20larger%20of%20the%20two%2C%20which%20houses%20a%20bunch%20of%20machines%2C%20including%20this%20one%20designed%20to%20perform%20a%20%26quot%3Bpull%20test.%26quot%3B%20They'll%20place%20a%20specimen%20of%20the%20paddle%20material%20between%20these%20two%20clamps%20and%20essentially%20rip%20it%20apart%20to%20test%20its%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20aerospace%20material%20science%2C%26quot%3B%20Tom%20told%20me%20%E2%80%94%20a%20phrase%20I%20never%20thought%20I'd%20include%20in%20the%20same%20sentence%20as%20%26quot%3Bpickleball.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22selkirk%20sport%20lab%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696aa17ea645d1188187891f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20showed%20me%20what's%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Boptical%20profilometer%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20digital%20microscope%20that%20lets%20you%20examine%20the%20paddle's%20face%20in%20detail.%20The%20texture%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20grit%20%E2%80%94%20on%20a%20paddle%20is%20important.%20It%20creates%20spin%20and%20influences%20ball%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20fancy%20microscope%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20can%20see%20every%20little%20crystal%20of%20our%20grit%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tom.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20see%20every%20dot%20of%20the%20ink%20on%20here.%20And%20we%20can%20see%20defects.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20much%20better%20photo%20of%20the%20machine%20than%20the%20one%20I%20snapped%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226336%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22selkrik%20sport%20lab%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696a9ee9e1ba468a96aa4099%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224217%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESelkirk%20Sport%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20up%20is%20my%20personal%20favorite%3A%20Thor's%20hammer.%20Tom%20describes%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20really%20fancy%20potato%20cannon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20scanning%20a%20fresh%20paddle%2C%20engineers%20will%20place%20it%20inside%20this%20big%2C%20red%20cage%2C%20and%20the%20durability%20cannon%20will%20fire%20pickleballs%20at%20it%20every%20six%20seconds%2C%20about%201%2C000%20times.%20Then%20it%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20profilometer%20for%20another%20scan%20to%20see%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20surface%20after%20all%20the%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20bulky%20machine%20they%20sourced%20from%20China%20and%20originally%20intended%20for%20tennis%20racket%20testing.%20Tom%20describes%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bbig%20and%20slow%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20gets%20the%20job%20done%20for%20now.%20He%20was%20excited%20to%20share%20that%20his%20team%20is%20working%20on%20their%20own%20version%20of%20Thor's%20hammer%20that%20will%20be%20smaller%20and%20fire%20balls%20even%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22selkirk%20sport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696a9f30c58df2ecd5ccb59e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20CT%20scanner%20in%20this%20room.%20While%20the%20profilometer%20performs%20an%20external%20scan%2C%20the%20CT%20performs%20an%20internal%20scan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20what%20he's%20looking%20for%20in%20the%20images.%20%26quot%3BEverything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20look%20at%20every%20microscopic%20detail%20inside%20the%20paddle%20and%20make%20sure%20everything%20is%20where%20we%20want%20it%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20they%20had%20the%20CT%20scanner%2C%20the%20only%20way%20they%20could%20see%20what%20was%20going%20on%20inside%20the%20paddle%20was%20to%20saw%20it%20open%20and%20manually%20inspect%20it.%20The%20method%20worked%2C%20but%20destroyed%20the%20paddle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20only%20do%20that%20once%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tom.%20Whereas%2C%20with%20the%20CT%20scanner%2C%20the%20paddle%20is%20still%20playable%20after%20the%20inspection.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20biggest%2C%20most%20important%20thing%20we've%20ever%20bought%20for%20non-destructive%20testing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221958%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22selkirk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696aa163c58df2ecd5ccb604%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221469%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%2C%20smaller%20room%20of%20the%20lab%20has%20machines%20that%20test%20for%20swing%20and%20twist%20weight.%20It%20also%20houses%20what%20Tom%20likes%20to%20call%20their%20%26quot%3Bacademic%20research%20cannon%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bperformance%20cannon.%26quot%3B%20Its%20main%20job%20is%20to%20help%20figure%20out%20the%20physics%20involved%20in%20the%20sport%3A%20What%20happens%20when%20a%20plastic%20ball%20hits%20a%20paddle%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Thor's%20hammer%2C%20it%20involves%20firing%20pickleballs%20at%20a%20stationary%20paddle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20measuring%20how%20efficient%20the%20collision%20is%2C%20which%20is%20basically%20how%20efficient%20the%20paddle%20is%20%E2%80%94%20not%20too%20dissimilar%20to%20how%20many%20miles%20a%20car%20can%20go%20on%20a%20gallon%20a%20gas%2C%26quot%3B%20said%