20enrollment%20declined%20by%203.5%20percent%20between%202025%20and%202026%20%E2%80%94%20entirely%20a%20result%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20commonsense%20measures%20to%20cut%20waste%2C%20fraud%2C%20and%20abuse%20and%20remove%20people%20who%20were%20improperly%20enrolled%20on%20highly-subsidized%20ACA%20plans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20renew%20these%20credits%20were%20a%20point%20of%20contention%20between%20Democrats%20and%20Republicans%20in%20Congress%2C%20contributing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-vote-government-reopened-longest-shutdown-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20latest%20government%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Lawmakers%20opted%20not%20to%20renew%20the%20subsidies%20in%20December%2C%20and%20the%20latest%20ACA%20vote%20is%20stalled%20in%20the%20Senate%20until%20late%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20have%20said%20they%20aim%20to%20reach%20a%20compromise%20healthcare%20strategy%2C%20but%20a%20plan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2026%2F01%2FThe-Great-Healthcare-Plan.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20on%20January%2015%20does%20not%20mention%20subsidies.%20The%20plan%20lays%20out%20the%20administration's%20goals%20to%20lower%20drug%20prices%20and%20insurance%20premiums%2C%20implement%20cost-sharing%20programs%2C%20and%20increase%20cost%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20basic%20contour%20of%20the%20plan%20is%20contradictory%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gideon%20Lukens%2C%20senior%20fellow%20and%20director%20of%20research%20and%20data%20analysis%20at%20the%20Center%20on%20Budget%20Policy%20and%20Priorities.%20%26quot%3BMuch%20less%20the%20question%20of%20how%20this%20would%20work%2C%20who%20would%20get%20what%2C%20and%20why%20this%20is%20better%20than%20directly%20covering%20people's%20premiums%20to%20prevent%20the%20spikes%20millions%20of%20people%20are%20facing%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22085bf7c9-ff5f-412c-aa5c-7e1cb5440738%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnalysts%20expect%20more%20people%20to%20drop%20ACA%20insurance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPolicy%20analysts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20expect%20a%20steeper%20decline%20in%20ACA%20enrollment%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months.%20The%20January%20report%20is%20a%20snapshot%20of%20the%20marketplace%20landscape%2C%20but%20comes%20with%20caveats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20data%20shows%20how%20many%20Americans%20selected%20a%20marketplace%20plan%20during%20open%20enrollment%20or%20were%20automatically%20renewed%20for%20their%20existing%20ACA%20coverage.%20It%20doesn't%20capture%20how%20many%20people%20have%20paid%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-soaring-healthcare-costs-are-changing-where-millionaires-move-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehealth%20insurance%20premiums%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20that%20more%20people%20are%20likely%20to%20drop%20coverage%20once%20they%20start%20receiving%20bills.%20A%20recent%20Congressional%20Budget%20Office%20report%20estimates%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbo.gov%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2F2025-09%2F61734-Health.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%204%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20Americans%20will%20lose%20or%20drop%20insurance%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20likely%20signed%20up%20when%20the%20premiums%20they%20would%20end%20up%20facing%20were%20uncertain%20and%20then%20waited%20to%20see%20what%20they%20would%20have%20to%20pay%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Matthew%20Buettgens%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20The%20Urban%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20few%20states%20where%20enrollment%20spiked%2C%20Fielder%20theorized%20that%20local%20healthcare%20policy%20is%20a%20factor.%20California%20offers%20its%20own%20ACA%20subsidies%2C%20for%20example%2C%20so%20residents%20are%20less%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20federal%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20direct%20impact%20on%20patients%2C%20Fielder%20also%20said%20the%20lapse%20of%20ACA%20credits%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fc-section-hospital-rates-differences-data-analysis-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eput%20more%20pressure%20on%20hospitals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20because%20providers%20could%20see%20an%20influx%20of%20uninsured%20patients%2C%20and%20people%20would%20be%20less%20likely%20to%20seek%20care%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20facilities%20that%20were%20already%20financially%20fragile%20for%20whom%20this%20is%20the%20straw%20that%20breaks%20the%20camel's%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmap-health-insurance-enrollment-dropped-affordable-care-act-subsidies-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1768644181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696a726cc58df2ecd5ccac25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmap-health-insurance-enrollment-dropped-affordable-care-act-subsidies-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ACA%20subsidies%20expiring%20leaves%201.4%20million%20fewer%20insured%20compared%20to%202025%2C%20as%20CMS%20data%20shows%20enrollment%20declines%20in%20Florida%20and%20other%20Southern%20states.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22allisonkelly%40businessinsider.com%20(Allie%20Kelly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmap-health-insurance-enrollment-dropped-affordable-care-act-subsidies-2026-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pooja%20Bhatt%20marks%2023%20years%20of%20%E2%80%98Jism%E2%80%99%20with%20John%20Abraham%20throwback%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1768643192000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2F